34
00:02:26,020 --> 00:02:27,730
because they never
get out of hand,

35
00:02:27,730 --> 00:02:31,720
they never overflow
or underflow.

36
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:35,890
And I'll put them
into a matrix Q,

37
00:02:35,890 --> 00:02:37,930
and then the second
part of the lecture

38
00:02:37,930 --> 00:02:42,130
will be suppose my
